#: ../../source/package-ecosystem.rst:2
msgid "Package Ecosystem Guide"
msgstr "包生态系统指南"

#: ../../source/package-ecosystem.rst:4
msgid ""
"Fabricatio is organized as a monorepo with 31 Python packages and 13 Rust"
" crates. This guide provides an overview of the ecosystem and helps you "
"understand which packages to use for your use case."
msgstr ""
"Fabricatio 以 monorepo 形式组织，包含 31 个 Python 包和 13 个 Rust "
"crate。本指南概述了整个生态系统，帮助你了解各包的用途以便选择合适的包。"

